subject: Football
lead_paragraph: Keeping the 49ers’ slim playoff hopes alive, Alex Smith threw two touchdown passes in the final quarter and visiting San Francisco prevented the Seattle Seahawks from clinching the National Football Conference West with a 24-14 victory last night.
